# API Conventions

- Thin route handlers: validate → call service → respond
- Zod parse at route boundary; never pass raw request deeper
- `requirePermission()` at entry (BB-PERM-01)
- JQL passed to Jira only, never interpolated into SQL (max 2000 chars)

## Error Responses (BB-API-01)

- 422: `{ message, errors: { field: [msgs] } }`
- 400/500: `{ success: false, message }`
- 409: `{ success: false, message, syncRunId }` (BB-SYNC-09)
- 403: sync-status ownership (BB-PERM-02)

## Routes

Register `/bug-budget/export/csv` BEFORE `/bug-budget/{id}` wildcard.
